English: You feel a chill, as if something has just entered your body...
Chinese: 身上好像有什么东西进来了一样的恶寒……

English: You feel an unpleasant sensation, writhing within your body...
Chinese: 身体中好像有什么在蠕动着的不快感……

English: You feel a prickling sensation, as if you were being pierced by pins and needles...
Chinese: 感觉身体的毛孔里好像被针扎进去一样地发冷……

English: A Snake... Just now, I saw a Snake.
